{"tid":1560400,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Escape Fome Tarkov，超真實既射精遊戲","createTime":"2019-09-11T07:35:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T04:46:10.000Z","uid":12228,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d0a1eb17814e7ba5884a715d4235fa5f189684da","tid":1560400,"uid":12228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T07:35:49.000Z","msg":"《Escape From Tarkov》 (逃離塔科夫)遊戲研發商 Battlestate Games 旗下Hardcord線上遊戲，遊戲結合左RPG同FPS，故事設定喺俄羅斯城市塔科夫，由於街道比俄羅斯軍方同聯合國武力嘅包圍，玩家要喺孤立的塔科夫尋找出路，玩家會面對致命的威脅，並且會搵出城市背後的秘密。<br />\n遊戲<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>FAQ</strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ: 隻GAME幾時上市?<br />\nA: 官方話2019係最後一年Close Beta，估計會係2020年上市<br />\n<br />\nQ: 點樣可以加入Close Beta玩住先?<br />\nA: 只要上官網購買Pre-Order就可以即刻玩<br />\n官網:<a href=\"https://www.escapefromtarkov.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.escapefromtarkov.com%2F&d=33lQL0pOg%2F%2Bbj%2F%2FH3PrIWYICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=5bf4eaeb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.escapefromtarkov.com/</a><br />\n<br />\nQ: Pre-Order版本有平有貴，有咩分別。<br />\nA: 越貴版本喺GAME入面主要個人倉庫會越大，可以放更多槍 配件 等等(因為GAME入面要你交任務物品會係煙仔/DISPLAY CARD等等嘅立雜物品)<br />\n可以參考巴哈:<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=29943&amp;snA=42\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D29943%26snA%3D42&d=33lQL0pOg%2F%2Bbj%2F%2FH3PrIWYICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=ea35f543\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=29943&amp;snA=42</a><br />\n<br />\nQ: 如果我一買就最貴但唔鐘意玩未曬錢...?<br />\nA: 怕自己唔鐘意但又想試下可以買最平/特價時購買試下<br />\n<br />\nQ: 會唔會有得升級版本?<br />\nA: 有，只要你補返差價就可以升級。<br />\n<br />\nQ: 有無Group 一齊玩?<br />\nA: Discord Group<a href=\"https://discord.gg/sFRZt7G\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2FsFRZt7G&d=33lQL0pOg%2F%2Bbj%2F%2FH3PrIWYICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=dae51979\" target=\"_blank\">https://discord.gg/sFRZt7G</a><br />\n<br />\nQ: 講咁多有無片睇下玩咩?<br />\nA: <br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6MWo5ecd3K0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6MWo5ecd3K0&d=33lQL0pOg%2F%2Bbj%2F%2FH3PrIWYICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=c40f8c50\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6MWo5ecd3K0</a><br />\n\t<br />\n\t 無香港人拍片 用住台灣人片先啦<br />\n<br />\n之後再更新新手入門"},{"pid":"2aaf7ac2bb3b45bb3dd29e9bd2612b76ce1ae111","tid":1560400,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T07:37:14.000Z","msg":"點解標題咁都可以串錯字<br />\n<br />\n我仲以為係俄文羅馬化"},{"pid":"6f6794c28d9d848a21e564d613caab29b380314f","tid":1560400,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T07:37:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GiW8u64.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGiW8u64.jpg&h=6e2a8a86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRrFcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dRrFcS</a>"},{"pid":"7c40279e3dcbe97e7c1a18d38a1ffae61a48d9e7","tid":1560400,"uid":12228,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"2aaf7ac2bb3b45bb3dd29e9bd2612b76ce1ae111","tid":1560400,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T07:37:14.000Z","msg":"點解標題咁都可以串錯字<br />\n<br />\n我仲以為係俄文羅馬化"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T07:37:53.000Z","msg":"對唔住，我係垃圾"},{"pid":"76dc1abfd3da69a94f902882ed3c10b7e28d585b","tid":1560400,"uid":205462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T07:40:11.000Z","msg":"玩得興奮，難免會有少少嘢漏出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b08927f27f5fa2f40bd54496ce4b73ddf922423b","tid":1560400,"uid":12228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76dc1abfd3da69a94f902882ed3c10b7e28d585b","tid":1560400,"uid":205462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T07:40:11.000Z","msg":"玩得興奮，難免會有少少嘢漏出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy